<paragraph id="682736A5FFADD47AFF61F2E7FC66FB87" blockId="50.[151,1437,654,1077]" pageId="50" pageNumber="51">
<emphasis id="5AECEAB7FFADD47AFF61F2E7FE04FC5E" bold="true" box="[199,444,978,1004]" pageId="50" pageNumber="51">General distribution</emphasis>
. Uncertain. Frecuently recorded in the Southeastern Asia (
<collectingCountry id="108F7635FFADD47AFBEEF2E6FB37FC5F" box="[1096,1167,979,1005]" name="China" pageId="50" pageNumber="51">China</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="108F7635FFADD47AFB3FF2E6FAF0FC5F" box="[1177,1352,979,1005]" name="Nepal Thailand" pageId="50" pageNumber="51">Nepal Thailand</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="108F7635FFADD47AFAF5F2E6FA2DFC5F" box="[1363,1429,979,1005]" name="Japan" pageId="50" pageNumber="51">Japan</collectingCountry>
) and 
<collectingCountry id="108F7635FFADD47AFF6EF2C2FE97FBA3" box="[200,303,1015,1041]" name="Australia" pageId="50" pageNumber="51">Australia</collectingCountry>
but will need verification due that this species is insufficiently described (
<bibRefCitation id="0C094B54FFADD47AFB33F2C2FA8BFBA3" author="Yoshii, R." box="[1173,1331,1014,1041]" pageId="50" pageNumber="51" pagination="51 - 68" refId="ref143994" refString="Yoshii, R. (1995 b) Identity of some Japanese Collembola III. Azao, Acta Zoologica Asiae Orientalis, 3, 51 - 68." type="journal article" year="1995">Yoshii 1995b</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="0C094B54FFADD47AFAE7F2C2FEDEFB87" author="Chen, J. X. &amp; Christiansen, K. A." pageId="50" pageNumber="51" pagination="1 - 19" refId="ref127944" refString="Chen, J. X. &amp; Christiansen, K. A. (1997) Subgenus Coecobrya of the genus Sinella (Collembola: Entomobryidae) with special reference to the species of China. Annals of the Entomological Society of America, 90, 1 - 19. https: // doi. org / 10.1093 / aesa / 90.1.1" type="journal article" year="1997">Chen &amp; Christiansen 1997</bibRefCitation>
). According to 
<bibRefCitation id="0C094B54FFADD47AFDB4F52EFD03FB87" author="Jordana, R." box="[530,699,1051,1077]" pageId="50" pageNumber="51" pagination="1 - 390" refId="ref132144" refString="Jordana, R. (2012) Capbryinae &amp; Entomobryini. In: Dunger, W. (Eds.), Synopses on Palaearctic Collembola. Soil Organisms, 84 (1), pp. 1 - 390." type="journal article" year="2012">Jordana (2012)</bibRefCitation>
it is an European species.
